---
title: "How Adults with Binge Eating Disorder May Present"
description: "Find info on binge eating disorder in adults, including diagnostic criteria, distinction from other eating disorders, prevalence, and possible causes."
keywords: ""
---

extends /layouts/base.jade

//- append analytics
    :raw

block content

    .gradient
    #gradient-transition-bottom

    section.section--carousel(ng-controller="ProfilesController as ProfCtrl")
        .wrap--content

            .carousel
                .slides
                    .slide.kimberly(ng-class="{active: currentSlide == 'kimberly'}" ng-swipe-left="swipeControls('R')" ng-swipe-right="swipeControls('L')")

                        +picture('profiles/kimberly.png',"Caucasian woman").hero
                        .mobile-hero
                        .shadow

                        blockquote
                            p.
                                I feel like I&rsquo;ve lost control while I&rsquo;m eating.

                        +mobile-carousel-pagination
                        .profile
                            .name.
                                Kimberly
                            .binge.
                                Average of 2 binge-eating episodes per week
                            .text-line
                                .age.
                                    Age: 34
                                .bmi.
                                    Body mass index (BMI): 29
                            .text-line
                                .stat.
                                    Kimberly works as a high school librarian
                                .stat.
                                    She is single and lives alone
                                .stat
                                    | Kimberly&rsquo;s binges are usually the 
                                    br
                                    | result of boredom
                            p.disclaimer
                                | Diagnosis should be based upon a complete evaluation of the patient that confirms the 
                                a(href="dsm5-criteria.aspx") criteria for !{BED}&nbsp;
                                | established in !{DSM5}.
                                sup 1

                    .slide.nikki(ng-class="{active : currentSlide == 'nikki'}" ng-swipe-left="swipeControls('R')" ng-swipe-right="swipeControls('L')")

                        +picture('profiles/nikki.png',"African American woman").hero
                        .mobile-hero

                        blockquote
                            p.
                                I&rsquo;m disgusted with myself after I binge.

                        +mobile-carousel-pagination

                        .profile
                            .name.
                                Nikki
                            .binge.
                                Average of 3 binge-eating episodes per week
                            .text-line
                                .age.
                                    Age: 27
                                .bmi.
                                    Body mass index (BMI): 28
                            .text-line
                                .stat.
                                    Nikki is a pediatric oncology nurse
                                .stat.
                                    Her binges are triggered by interpersonal stressors
                                .stat.
                                    Nikki is distressed by her bingeing behavior

                            p.disclaimer
                                | Diagnosis should be based upon a complete evaluation of the patient that confirms the 
                                a(href="dsm5-criteria.aspx") criteria for !{BED}&nbsp;
                                | established in !{DSM5}.
                                sup 1

                    .slide.julie(ng-class="{active : currentSlide == 'julie'}" ng-swipe-left="swipeControls('R')" ng-swipe-right="swipeControls('L')")

                        +picture('profiles/julie.png','Caucasian woman').hero
                        .mobile-hero

                        blockquote
                            p.
                                When the binges are over, I feel guilty about my behavior.

                        +mobile-carousel-pagination

                        .profile
                            .name.
                                Julie
                            .binge.
                                Average of 5 binge-eating episodes per week
                            .text-line
                                .age.
                                    Age: 42
                                .bmi.
                                    Body mass index (BMI): 35
                            .text-line
                                .stat.
                                    Julie works as an advertising executive
                                .stat.
                                    Her binges are triggered by negative feelings about her body shape
                                .stat.
                                    Julie has a coexisting psychiatric disorder&mdash;she struggles with anxiety

                            p.disclaimer
                                | Diagnosis should be based upon a complete evaluation of the patient that confirms the 
                                a(href="dsm5-criteria.aspx") criteria for !{BED}&nbsp;
                                | established in !{DSM5}.
                                sup 1

                    .slide.diego(ng-class="{active : currentSlide == 'diego'}" ng-swipe-left="swipeControls('R')" ng-swipe-right="swipeControls('L')")

                        +picture('profiles/diego.png','Latino man').hero
                        //- .mobile-hero
                        //- .shadow

                        blockquote
                            p
                                | I binge alone because I don&rsquo;t want anyone 
                                br.desktop-break
                                span to know how much I eat.

                        +mobile-carousel-pagination

                        .profile
                            .name.
                                Diego
                            .binge.
                                Average of 8 binge-eating episodes per week
                            .text-line
                                .age.
                                    Age: 30
                                .bmi.
                                    Body mass index (BMI): 32
                            .text-line
                                .stat.
                                    Diego works a second night-shift job to help support his family
                                .stat.
                                    Following his binges, Diego tends to feel depressed

                            p.disclaimer
                                | Diagnosis should be based upon a complete evaluation of the patient that confirms the 
                                a(href="dsm5-criteria.aspx") criteria for !{BED}&nbsp;
                                | established in !{DSM5}.

                .controls
                    .prev(ng-click="clickControls('L')" hover-carousel-control)
                    .next(ng-click="clickControls('R')" hover-carousel-control)

                

                ul.pagination
                    li.kimberly(ng-click="changeHero('kimberly')", scroll-to="")
                        | kimberly
                        span.liner
                    li.nikki(ng-click="changeHero('nikki')", scroll-to="")
                        | nikki
                        span.liner
                    li.julie(ng-click="changeHero('julie')", scroll-to="")
                        | julie
                        span.liner
                    li.diego(ng-click="changeHero('diego')", scroll-to="")
                        | diego

            p.section-disclaimer-sm.
                Models and descriptions are fictional representations of how some adults with !{BED} may present and do not constitute the totality of !{BED} symptoms and criteria.

            .callouts
                .callout.one
                    h2.heading--2.
                        Screening the patient
                    p.
                        Use this validated screener to help evaluate adult patients you suspect may have !{BED}
                    a(href="media/BingeEatingDisorder_Screener.pdf",target="_blank").btn.btn--blue.authorized-link.
                        DOWNLOAD THE ADULT !{BED} PATIENT SCREENER
                .callout.two
                    h2.heading--2.
                        Conducting a conversation
                    p.
                        Use this discussion guide to help begin a dialogue about !{BED} with your adult patients.
                    a(href="media/BingeEatingDisorderDiscussionGuide.pdf",target="_blank").btn.btn--blue.authorized-link.
                        DOWNLOAD THE DISCUSSION GUIDE FOR ADULT PATIENTS WITH !{BED}

            p.section-disclaimer
                | These tools were developed by Shire to assist health care professionals in identifying and accurately diagnosing !{BED} in adults.

            .wrap--refs
                ol.refs.number
                    li
                        | American Psychiatric Association. Binge-eating disorder. In: 
                        em Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders. 
                        | 5th ed. Arlington, VA: American Psychiatric Association; 2013:350-353.


